name: Duskfall Virtual 3D Diffusion
description:
Duskfall Virtual 3D Diffusion

If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

A base checkpoint that's better suited for MERGING than basic use. Your best options are to use OCTANE RENDER, Unreal Engine style prompts along side the key trigger.


If you like what we've got for our merged and other models consider donating: https://patreon.com/earthndusk

  • DO NOT SELL THIS MODEL, OR MERGES

  • Do merge, and do enjoy.

  • Generative images for commercial use are fine.

  • Credit in your merges would be great.

Examples of the training images:

Data Info: We modeled (or created) these over time with money we spent in the virtual world. Literally have likely spent 100s if not 1000s of dollars over a decade with this LOL. It was only about 65 images.

modelVersions.description:
This is going to be for now the only version unless other MERGED editions come out. That is of course unless I train another one and then i'll just merge it with this one.

EDIT: Added safetensors.
